</th></tr>
<tr>
<td>Grade
</td>
<td>Grade
</td>
<td>ENUM
</td>
<td>Grades
</td></tr>
</tbody></table>
<p>Then add the entity links for the Class and the Student (which links to the Person record type).
</p><p><br>
Field Name	Multilingual label	Logical type	Reference to
Class	Class	ENTITY_LINK	Class
Student	Student	ENTITY_LINK	Person
</p>
